name: Shinobi III: Return of the Ninja Master
storyline: Joe Musashis sworn enemy the Neo Zeed are secretly rebuilding an organization in Japan after the battle in Neo City Joe code name Shinobi senses the evil power growing and starts to make his way back to fight the Neo Zeed once again
summary: Shinobi III Return of the Ninja Master released as The Super Shinobi II in Japan is the fourth game in the Shinobi series and a direct sequel to The Revenge of Shinobi
